olds that govern whether a star turns into a black hole (自己去查，呢度唔多講) swatzchild radius and critical mass)<br />\n<br />\noh and also 粒子唔會重疊，同埋更高維度真係jm9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2)點解粒子變唔到黑洞<br />\nthis question is 100% on9 tbh, and dark matter has nothing to do with this. <br />\n<br />\nhow particles work is govern by strong and weak force, go check wikipedia<br />\n<br />\n伸利9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8abaf1bbecacdefed6f788f7eb706899c7785e47","tid":787876,"uid":61484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d26a6dfbc2fe417be4aef2b44f352b7bb8cf6fdd","tid":787876,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T04:45:26.000Z","msg":"古典睇法<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Classical_electron_radius\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FClassical_electron_radius&d=AIB9wnxRt8rjcHg3QClxIVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=4a858c15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Classical_electron_radius</a><br />\n<br />\n現代睇法<br />\n好似係視界短過普朗克長度 好似係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T05:13:39.000Z","msg":"視界&lt;普朗克長度 <br />\n呢個statenent是咪代表緊個粒子=黑洞=量子(不能測量)<br />\n<br />\n純粹問問，等睇物理高手一巴車埋黎"},{"pid":"87747745983228fc022230386f513053e76d717e","tid":787876,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8abaf1bbecacdefed6f788f7eb706899c7785e47","tid":787876,"uid":61484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d26a6dfbc2fe417be4aef2b44f352b7bb8cf6fdd","tid":787876,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T04:45:26.000Z","msg":"古典睇法<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Classical_electron_radius\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FClassical_electron_radius&d=AIB9wnxRt8rjcHg3QClxIVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=4a858c15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Classical_electron_radius</a><br />\n<br />\n現代睇法<br />\n好似係視界短過普朗克長度 好似係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T05:13:39.000Z","msg":"視界&lt;普朗克長度 <br />\n呢個statenent是咪代表緊個粒子=黑洞=量子(不能測量)<br />\n<br />\n純粹問問，等睇物理高手一巴車埋黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T05:21:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/微型黑洞\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E5%BE%AE%E5%9E%8B%E9%BB%91%E6%B4%9E&d=AIB9wnxRt8rjcHg3QClxIVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=36659ba3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/微型黑洞</a><br />\n<br />\n要製造一個黑洞，我們必須要集中質量或能量到逃脫速率超過光速的程度。這個狀況給出了史瓦西半徑公式R=2GM/c^2，這裡G是牛頓常數，c是光速，M是黑洞的質量。另外，康普頓波長（&lambda;=ℏ/Mc）代表了質量M在靜止時可以被定位的最小範圍。對足夠小的M，縮小後的康普頓波長超過了史瓦西半徑的一半，而這樣則無法存在有關此黑洞的描述（因為無法被定位）。因此可以推斷出，最小的黑洞質量大約是普朗克質量。"},{"pid":"82f4a2e2fd2a8839a2b0fc83fc36d6eb30fdf72b","tid":787876,"uid":67645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T05:34:10.000Z","msg":"據說subatomic particle係point particle<br />\n得質量冇體積<br />\n同埋好似電子要有spin又要有體積好似個需要個形狀係無限長嘅cylinder<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講就係好多classical嘅概念都apply唔到落quantum level<br />\n<br />\n利申 好似係咁"},{"pid":"dac33267a8ed631ad8d99b30c85774a38ed3885c","tid":787876,"uid":61484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87747745983228fc022230386f513053e76d717e","tid":787876,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8abaf1bbecacdefed6f788f7eb706899c7785e47","tid":787876,"uid":61484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d26a6dfbc2fe417be4aef2b44f352b7bb8cf6fdd","tid":787876,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T04:45:26.000Z","msg":"古典睇法<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Classical_electron_radius\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FClassical_electron_radius&d=AIB9wnxRt8rjcHg3QClxIVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=4a858c15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wi